query:
SELECT id, messageId, team1, team2, team1Players, team2Players, status, upvotes, downvotes, createdAt, processedAt, reversedAt 
FROM trades 
WHERE team1Players LIKE '%Zach LaVine%' OR team2Players LIKE '%Zach LaVine%'
   OR team1Players LIKE '%Luguentz Dort%' OR team2Players LIKE '%Luguentz Dort%'
ORDER BY createdAt DESC 
LIMIT 10
